"Plural-Forms: nplurals=2; plural=(n != 1);\n"

msgid "古老的祭坛泛起微光，符文如呼吸般明灭。随着空中清脆的声音叮当一声，一个温柔的女声在你耳畔响起"
msgstr "The ancient altar glows softly, runes pulsing like breath. A gentle female voice whispers in your ear..."

msgid "旅人，以爱与誓约换取力量… 献上汝之祭品。"
msgstr "Traveler, trade love and vows for power... Offer your sacrifice."

msgid "选择吧… 代价即荣耀。（请注意读档后设定该加成会消失）"
msgstr "Choose... The cost is glory. (Note: this bonus resets on reload.)"

msgid "你的财富（500gold）"
msgstr "Your wealth (500 gold)"

msgid "带着真挚情感的物品"
msgstr "An item of true sentiment"

msgid "取消"
msgstr "Cancel"

msgid "一道柔光将你的身体笼罩，你感觉到了力量在涌动。"
msgstr "A soft light envelops you; you feel power surging within."

msgid "所有的一切都需要代价。"
msgstr "Everything comes at a price."

msgid "乌诺: 我好痛啊！全身都在腐烂……却不会死去，这或许就是代价"
msgstr "Uno: It hurts so much! My body rots... yet I cannot die. Perhaps this is the price."

msgid "乌诺: 我的药只差一步就要完成了……但一切都是无用之力……谎言！"
msgstr "Uno: My medicine was almost complete... but it's all futile... Lies!"

msgid "乌诺: 勇士，选择很多，但是真正的道路只有一条。"
msgstr "Uno: Brave one, there are many choices, but only one true path."

msgid "他死的时候，仅剩的魔力点燃了他的躯体"
msgstr "As he dies, his last remnants of magic ignite his body."

msgid "乌诺: 只有这样才能不让瘟疫扩散开来"
msgstr "Uno: Only this way can the plague be contained."

msgid "在他死后，一颗炙热的红宝石般剔透的心脏留在了原地，你走过去将它捡起"
msgstr "After his death, a ruby-like heart, burning bright, remains. You walk over and pick it up."

msgid "书架上摆满了魔法书，你一个字也看不懂。直到你仔细翻查，在角落里发现了记忆药水和一页笔记。"
msgstr "The shelves are lined with spellbooks, all in a language you can't read. After searching thoroughly, you find a Memory Potion and a page of notes in the corner."

msgid "你发现了巫师的一则手记。"
msgstr "You find a wizard's journal entry."

msgid "地上的骸骨属于一个孩子。他得了疫病，为了不感染其他人，小孩选择独自出走，遇到了巫师。"
msgstr "The bones on the ground belong to a child. Stricken by plague, the child left alone to protect others, and crossed paths with the wizard."

msgid "巫师带着他来到魔塔中，一边研究一边尝试治疗他。"
msgstr "The wizard brought the child into the magic tower, studying and trying to cure him."

msgid "可惜，还没来得及痊愈，小孩就死了，巫师也受到了感染。"
msgstr "Alas, before the child could be healed, he died. The wizard too became infected."

msgid "你发现了巫师的一则手记，上面记录着魔法。"
msgstr "You find a wizard's journal entry detailing a spell."

msgid "没有什么可以探查的了"
msgstr "There's nothing left to investigate."

msgid "进入第一层"
msgstr "Entering Floor 1"

msgid "进入第二层"
msgstr "Entering Floor 2"

msgid "进入第三层"
msgstr "Entering Floor 3"

msgid "进入第四层"
msgstr "Entering Floor 4"

msgid "进入第五层"
msgstr "Entering Floor 5"

msgid "进入第六层"
msgstr "Entering Floor 6"

msgid "进入第七层"
msgstr "Entering Floor 7"

msgid "进入第八层"
msgstr "Entering Floor 8"

msgid "进入第九层"
msgstr "Entering Floor 9"

msgid "进入第十层"
msgstr "Entering Floor 10"

msgid "进入隐秘的房间"
msgstr "Entering the Secret Room"

msgid "商人: 你好，勇士。要买点什么吗？"
msgstr "Merchant: Hello, brave one. Looking to buy something?"

msgid "商人: 你的选择没错"
msgstr "Merchant: A fine choice."

msgid "商人: 真有眼光"
msgstr "Merchant: You have good taste."

msgid "商人: 下次见，亲爱的勇士"
msgstr "Merchant: See you next time, dear customer."

msgid "黄色钥匙	200gold"
msgstr "Yellow Key	200 gold"

msgid "普通的铁剑	1000gold"
msgstr "Iron Sword	1000 gold"

msgid "离开"
msgstr "Leave"

msgid "hello"
msgstr "hello"

msgid "get out"
msgstr "get out"

msgid "一瞬间，一股冰凉的寒意窜上你的头颅，你感受到了一阵撕裂般的剧痛。"
msgstr "A sudden chill surges through your skull; you feel a tearing pain."

msgid "一些片段从你的脑海里一闪而逝……"
msgstr "Fragments flash through your mind..."

msgid "你什么都没有抓到。"
msgstr "You grasp nothing."

msgid "勇士: ……"
msgstr "Brave: ..."

msgid "又是一阵头疼，忍过剧痛之后，这一次你凝神捕获那些出现在你脑海中的记忆碎片……"
msgstr "Another headache. After enduring the pain, you focus and catch the memory fragments surfacing in your mind..."

msgid "洁白的仪器发出滴滴的声音，在一片纯白的空间之中，一切都是死寂，只有另一个人的心跳声伴随着你。"
msgstr "White instruments beep softly. In this pure white space, all is silent except for another heartbeat keeping you company."

msgid "那些画面逐渐清晰起来，过去的一切在这一刻变得清晰"
msgstr "The images grow clearer. Everything from the past becomes vivid in this moment."

msgid "勇士: 你现在在看着我吗？"
msgstr "Brave: Are you watching me right now?"

msgid "勇士: 我已经知道该如何做出选择。"
msgstr "Brave: I already know how to choose."

msgid "这是一具骸骨，看身形应该是个十岁的孩子。"
msgstr "These are a child's bones — about ten years old, by the look of it."

msgid "要为他收敛骸骨吗？"
msgstr "Would you like to gather the bones for burial?"

msgid "好的"
msgstr "Yes"

msgid "说服失败了"
msgstr "Persuasion failed."

msgid "勇士: 费诺娜"
msgstr "Brave: Fenona"

msgid "神: 你的敌人会阻挡你，请无畏地前进并摧毁他们！打败魔塔之主，拯救世界，成为这个世界的英雄吧！"
msgstr "God: Enemies will block your path. Press forward fearlessly and crush them! Defeat the Tower Lord, save the world, become its hero!"

msgid "神: 世界需要你，请打败魔塔之主，拯救这个世界吧！"
msgstr "God: The world needs you. Defeat the Tower Lord and save us all!"

msgid "你已经死亡，神会给你重生的机会"
msgstr "You have died. God grants you a chance to be reborn."

msgid "你被神杀死了"
msgstr "You were slain by God."

msgid "神: 勇士只许死亡，不许投降，重来一次吧"
msgstr "God: A hero may die, but never surrender. Try again."

msgid "神: 接下来的敌人会更厉害，要小心了！"
msgstr "God: The enemies ahead are stronger. Be careful!"

msgid "神: 接下来你要走好运了！"
msgstr "God: Good fortune is coming your way!"

msgid "教程: 方向键移动，ESC设置，I背包"
msgstr "Tutorial: Arrow keys to move, ESC for settings, I for inventory."

msgid "进入第1层"
msgstr "Entering Floor 1"

msgid "感谢你完成了本游戏，希望你有一场愉快的冒险。"
msgstr "Thank you for completing the game! We hope you enjoyed the adventure."

msgid "有任何事宜和评论，请联系我的邮箱：anystarworld@qq.com，或者加我的QQ2056681440，谢谢。"
msgstr "For any inquiries or feedback, please email: anystarworld@qq.com, or QQ: 2056681440. Thank you!"

msgid "当你打开门的一刻，你看到一道白光朝你而来"
msgstr "As you open the door, a blinding white light rushes toward you."

msgid "那不知名的掌声再次响起，伴随着嘘声."
msgstr "Mysterious applause rings out again, mixed with jeers."

msgid "制作人A: 恭喜你们，优秀员工奖非你们莫属！无比精彩的表演，许多观众为你们落泪，你们的演绎将成为珍珠，挂在宇宙娱乐圈巅峰的桂冠上。"
msgstr "Producer A: Congratulations! The 'Outstanding Employee' award is yours! A magnificent performance — many in the audience wept. Your art will shine like a pearl on the crown of the cosmic entertainment industry."

msgid "投资者B: 无可救药的演员工厂人，早就应该将你们销毁！失控又失控！不听话的工厂人有什么用！害我输了一大笔钱！"
msgstr "Investor B: Hopeless factory actors! You should have been scrapped long ago! Out of control! What use are disobedient factory workers?! You cost me a fortune!"

msgid "他气的双手发抖，机械关节渗出昂贵的机油。"
msgstr "His hands tremble with rage; expensive oil seeps from his mechanical joints."

msgid "老板: B你先别生气，这次虽然有许多差评，但是收视率非常高。"
msgstr "Boss: B, calm down. Sure, there were bad reviews, but the ratings are through the roof."

msgid "作为庄家的老板两头通吃，赚得盆满钵满。"
msgstr "The boss plays both sides and rakes in a fortune."

msgid "老板: 下面说一下结果吧。"
msgstr "Boss: Let's get to the results."

msgid "制作人A: 勇士和魔塔之主，你们通过了我们的考验。根据赌约，如果你们中只有一个人能够走出这扇门，那么另一个人就会被销毁。"
msgstr "Producer A: Brave and Tower Lord — you've passed our test. Per the bet: if only one of you walks through that door, the other will be scrapped."

msgid "制作人A: 但是或许有人不知道，我们的赌约还有另一部分，那就是，如果两位都出来，那么我就会帮你们申报，获得公民身份。"
msgstr "Producer A: But what some don't know is — the bet has another clause. If you BOTH walk out, I'll file for you to gain citizenship."

msgid "魔塔之主和勇者曾是最畅销的恋人搭档，但是观众很快就厌倦了他们的恩爱，希望他们反目成仇，于是他们相互厮杀直到另一方死亡，再由工厂重新复活。"
msgstr "The Tower Lord and the Brave were once a bestselling lover duo. But audiences grew tired of their romance and wanted to see them turn on each other — so they fought until one died, only to be revived by the factory."

msgid "有一天，当他们意识到了自己不过是他人手中的傀儡，进行了反抗，投资人厌恶不听话的工厂人，镇压了他们。"
msgstr "One day, they realized they were merely puppets. They rebelled. The investors, despising disobedient factory workers, crushed them."

msgid "最终他们被洗去记忆，扔进了废弃仓库。"
msgstr "In the end, their memories were wiped and they were discarded into an abandoned warehouse."

msgid "而金牌制作人A决定启用他们，说服老板为他们搭建一个舞台，一次次的重启，选择，以此为赌注让场外的观众们下注，造就了无比精彩的表演。"
msgstr "But Producer A decided to use them again, convincing the boss to build a stage. Reset after reset, choice after choice — the audience outside placed their bets, creating a spectacular show."

msgid "这一次让他再一次地看到了曾经荧屏上演员的风采。"
msgstr "This time, he saw the old screen legends shine once more."

msgid "无论他们属于哪里，他将为他们争取权益。"
msgstr "No matter where they belong, he will fight for their rights."

msgid "（镜头聚焦在勇士和魔塔之主身上，他们同时看向对方，魔塔之主轻轻点头）"
msgstr "(The camera focuses on the Brave and the Tower Lord. They look at each other; the Tower Lord nods softly.)"

msgid "制片人A: 这次，请为自己而活。"
msgstr "Producer A: This time — live for yourselves."

msgid "（画面渐暗，出现演职员表）"
msgstr "(The screen fades to credits.)"

msgid "恶魔——杰姆；药剂师——莉娜；徘徊的幽灵——无名者；巫师——乌诺；魔塔之主——菲欧娜"
msgstr "Devil — Jim; Alchemist — Lina; Wandering Ghost — The Nameless One; Wizard — Uno; Tower Lord — Fiona"

msgid "神: 那么到这里，故事就结束了。"
msgstr "God: And so, the story comes to an end."

msgid "摄像机红灯打过，工厂人瞳孔闪过着属于人类的虹膜色彩"
msgstr "The camera's red light flickers. For a moment, the factory worker's eyes flash with the iris of a human."

msgid "一行小字浮现：“本片未使用AI演员，以保护合法权益”"
msgstr "A small line appears: "No AI actors were used in this production, to protect legal rights.""

msgid "她看了你一眼，转过身……  "
msgstr "She glances at you, then turns away..."

msgid "神给了你重生的机会 "
msgstr "God grants you a chance to be reborn."

msgid "你成功打败了魔塔之主，拿到了白色的钥匙，当你打开门的一刻，你看到一道白光朝你而来"
msgstr "You defeated the Tower Lord and claimed the White Key. As you open the door, a blinding white light rushes toward you."

msgid "那不知名的掌声再次响起，神的声音在你耳畔响起"
msgstr "Mysterious applause rings out again, and God's voice echoes in your ear."

msgid "神: 恭喜你，你成功打败了魔塔之主，成为了这个世界的英雄"
msgstr "God: Congratulations! You have defeated the Tower Lord and become the hero of this world."

msgid "你仿佛听见自己的胸腔中跳动的声音，一切都是如此熟悉。"
msgstr "You feel a heartbeat resonance in your chest — everything feels so familiar."

msgid "一只毛色乌黑杂乱的老狗蜷缩在巷角，耷拉着的耳朵沾满泥浆，湿漉漉的红色眼睛蒙着白翳，破旧项圈半埋在蓬松的颈毛里。它用磨损的爪尖有气无力地扒拉着骨头，喉间挤出断续呜咽，尾巴在石板地上扫过。"
msgstr "A shaggy black mutt cowers in the alley corner. Mud-caked ears droop low; its wet red eyes are clouded with film. A frayed collar is half-buried in its matted fur. It paws feebly at a bone with worn claws, letting out broken whimpers as its tail sweeps the stone floor."

msgid "杰姆: 勇士，请帮帮我，我是可怜的人，被邪恶的魔塔之主变成了一条狗。"
msgstr "Jim: Brave, please help me! I'm a poor soul turned into a dog by the evil Tower Lord."

msgid "杰姆: 第三层的药剂师手中有解除变形药水，请把它给我 "
msgstr "Jim: The Alchemist on Floor 3 has a Deformation Relief Potion. Please bring it to me."

msgid "杰姆: 那个药剂师，她可是欠了我许多债躲到了这里，我是为了追债来的"
msgstr "Jim: That Alchemist owes me a lot of money and fled here. I'm just collecting my debt."

msgid "杰姆: 你拿到药水了吗？"
msgstr "Jim: Did you get the potion?"

msgid "杰姆: 我看看，你拿到药水了？快给我，拿走你的奖励"
msgstr "Jim: Let me see — you got it? Hand it over! Take your reward."

msgid "杰姆: 告诉你一个秘密，药剂师是一个女巫，她欠了我很多钱跑了！多么邪恶的人！如果你能打败她，就可以拿到她的药水和配方！"
msgstr "Jim: Let me tell you a secret — the Alchemist is a witch! She racked up a huge debt and ran off! If you beat her, you can claim all her potions and recipes!"

msgid "杰姆: 你杀了她？我的小可爱，你终于还是死了，我要去取走你的灵魂。"
msgstr "Jim: You killed her? My dear little thing, you're finally dead. Time to collect your soul."

msgid "杰姆: 哦，对了，这是一点谢礼，能帮助你打败魔塔之主。"
msgstr "Jim: Oh, right — here's a little gift to help you defeat the Tower Lord."

msgid "要和它战斗吗?"
msgstr "Fight it?"

msgid "战斗 "
msgstr "Fight"

msgid "杰姆: 愚蠢的东西，你竟然相信那个女巫说的话！ "
msgstr "Jim: You fool! You actually believed that witch?!"

msgid "杰姆: 这次算你赢了！下次你可没那么好运了！"
msgstr "Jim: You win this round! Next time you won't be so lucky!"

msgid "一位棕色卷发束成高马尾的圆脸女药剂师，雀斑点缀的笑脸泛着红晕。她身穿洗得发白的绿色亚麻长袍，外罩缝满口袋的靛蓝围裙。此刻她左手高举冒着绿烟的锥形瓶，踮脚前倾的身体几乎要探出橡木柜台，晶亮的榛子色眼珠紧追着滚动的钱币，咧开的嘴角扬起狡黠的弧度。"
msgstr "A round-faced young woman with brown hair tied in a high ponytail. Freckles dot her flushed cheeks. She wears a faded green linen robe under a blue apron stuffed with pockets. In her left hand, she hoists a smoking flask of green vapor, leaning so far over the oak counter she might topple. Her hazel eyes track a rolling coin with delight, a sly grin spreading across her face."

msgid "要和她战斗吗?"
msgstr "Fight her?"

msgid "药剂师: 你要打败我？来试试吧！ "
msgstr "Alchemist: You want to fight me? Come on, then!"

msgid "药剂师: 你就是那个传说中的勇士？要不要看一看我这里的东西？"
msgstr "Alchemist: So you're the legendary Brave? Want to browse my wares?"

msgid "药剂师: 嗨，勇士，来看一看我的商品吧！"
msgstr "Alchemist: Hey, Brave! Come check out my goods!"

msgid "你成功了！太好了！"
msgstr "You did it! Great!"

msgid "制作"
msgstr "Craft"

msgid "解除变形药水"
msgstr "Deformation Relief Potion"

msgid "药剂师: 我需要3个【蓝色草药】，收你150gold"
msgstr "Alchemist: I need 3 Blue Herbs. That'll be 150 gold."

msgid "确认"
msgstr "Confirm"

msgid "生命药水"
msgstr "Health Potion"

msgid "药剂师: 它能为你增加50点生命，我需要1个【红色草药】，收你100gold"
msgstr "Alchemist: It'll restore 50 HP. I need 1 Red Herb. That'll be 100 gold."

msgid "永恒药水"
msgstr "Perpetual Potion"

msgid "药剂师: 它能让你的生命力翻倍。我需要1颗【永恒的心】和3个【红色草药】，收你300gold"
msgstr "Alchemist: It'll double your vitality. I need 1 Eternal Heart and 3 Red Herbs. That'll be 300 gold."

msgid "现形药水"
msgstr "Revealing Potion"

msgid "药剂师: 它能让整个层的陷阱现形。我需要5个【蓝色草药】，收你100gold"
msgstr "Alchemist: It'll reveal all traps on the floor. I need 5 Blue Herbs. That'll be 100 gold."

msgid "购买"
msgstr "Buy"

msgid "看起来你身上的东西不足，准备好了再来找我吧。"
msgstr "Looks like you don't have enough. Come back when you're ready."

msgid "好好使用它"
msgstr "Use it well."

msgid "药剂师: 你是个慷慨大方又努力的人，我宣布我们是朋友了。但是抱歉我还是不会打折的。"
msgstr "Alchemist: You're generous and hardworking. I declare us friends! But sorry — still no discounts."

msgid "药剂师: 如果你遇到杰姆，千万别相信他说的话，他是一个恶魔，如果你可以杀了他，我会奖励你的"
msgstr "Alchemist: If you run into Jim, don't believe a word he says. He's a demon. If you can kill him, I'll reward you."

msgid "药剂师: 你有见过第4层的那个幽灵吗？它是个疯子，总是在说些奇怪的话。"
msgstr "Alchemist: Have you seen that ghost on Floor 4? He's crazy — always muttering strange things."

msgid "药剂师: 好吧，今天还是要看一看吗？"
msgstr "Alchemist: Alright, still want to browse today?"

msgid "药剂师: 非常感谢你！这是给你的奖励！这枚戒指是珍贵之物，请好好珍惜。"
msgstr "Alchemist: Thank you so much! This is your reward. This ring is precious — please treasure it."

msgid "药剂师: 你想知道我的故事？好的，这个故事说来话长。"
msgstr "Alchemist: You want to hear my story? Alright — it's a long one."

msgid "药剂师: 我出生在一个农户家庭，虽然我们的家很小，但一切都很幸福。"
msgstr "Alchemist: I was born into a farming family. Our home was small, but we were happy."

msgid "药剂师: 不知道从什么时候开始，镇上的魔物变多了，哥哥是镇上的护卫经常受伤，所以我决定未来要成为一个药剂师，这样我就可以帮助哥哥了。"
msgstr "Alchemist: Then monsters started appearing in town. My brother, a town guard, kept getting hurt — so I decided to become an alchemist to help him."

msgid "药剂师: 事情在我十六岁那年发生了变故。"
msgstr "Alchemist: Everything changed when I turned sixteen."

msgid "那年莉娜从药师学院毕业，一场天火从天而降，将她的故乡烧毁。她的父母葬送在天火中，哥哥和妹妹受了重伤，为了救回唯一的亲人，莉娜花光了自己身上所有的积蓄。"
msgstr "The year Lina graduated from alchemy school, a heavenly fire rained down and burned her hometown to ash. Her parents perished. Her brother and sister were gravely injured. To save her only remaining family, Lina spent every last coin she had."

msgid "药剂师: 即使我将自己身上的珍贵的东西都卖了，也支付不起神殿昂贵的治疗费。"
msgstr "Alchemist: Even after selling everything I treasured, I couldn't afford the Temple's steep treatment fees."

msgid "走投无路之下，一个乡绅上门来找她，借了她一笔钱。"
msgstr "Desperate, a country squire came to her door and offered a loan."

msgid "药剂师: 那个人就是杰姆。那时我并不知道他是一个恶魔！契约纸被动了手脚，如果我偿还不起就会被取走灵魂，神殿会因此判我亵渎神明，烧死我的亲人！"
msgstr "Alchemist: That man was Jim. I didn't know he was a demon! The contract was rigged — if I couldn't pay, my soul would be claimed, and the Temple would brand me a blasphemer and burn my family alive!"

msgid "莉娜从此之后日复一日干活，从没有一天休息，即使这样，债务却还是像滚雪球一般膨胀。她绝望地踏入黑暗森林，来到魔塔之下。"
msgstr "Day after day, Lina worked without rest. Even so, the debt snowballed. In despair, she entered the Dark Forest and arrived at the foot of the Magic Tower."

msgid "她没有勇气了结自我，所以不如被魔塔之主杀死，这样至少她的家人或许还有神殿赔偿。"
msgstr "She didn't have the courage to end her own life — so better to be killed by the Tower Lord. At least her family might get compensation from the Temple."

msgid "魔塔之主: ……"
msgstr "Tower Lord: ..."

msgid "药剂师: 魔塔之主出现了，她告诉我，如果我愿意，可以进入魔塔之中，在这里恶魔不敢伤害我。"
msgstr "Alchemist: The Tower Lord appeared. She told me I could enter the tower — here, no demon would dare harm me."

msgid "药剂师: 你来啦，我的朋友。"
msgstr "Alchemist: You're here, my friend."

msgid "药剂师: 永恒的心是非常稀有的物品，如果你有，一定要好好地保存。"
msgstr "Alchemist: The Eternal Heart is incredibly rare. If you have one, guard it well."

msgid "药剂师: 那个幽灵吗？它好像是来魔塔找人的，不知道为什么连自己都忘记了。可惜我所有的记忆药水被巫师拿走了。"
msgstr "Alchemist: That ghost? He came to the tower looking for someone, but even forgot himself. Unfortunately, the wizard took all my Memory Potions."

msgid "药剂师: 所有人都说这些灾难都是因为魔塔之主的存在，只有杀死魔塔之主，我们才能够得到拯救。你是怎么觉得，勇士？"
msgstr "Alchemist: Everyone says the disasters are the Tower Lord's doing — that only by killing her can we be saved. What do you think, Brave?"

msgid "药剂师: 为什么？我们不是朋友吗？"
msgstr "Alchemist: Why? Weren't we friends?"

msgid "药剂师: 我完蛋了！你害惨我了，我做鬼都不会放过你！！！"
msgstr "Alchemist: I'm finished! You've ruined me! I'll haunt you forever!!!"

msgid "药剂师: 她死了，你可以离开魔塔了。"
msgstr "Alchemist: She's dead. You can leave the tower now."

msgid "药剂师: 魔塔之主不让我告诉你，是她让我在这里卖药给你的，包括永恒药水，可是现在说已经太晚了。"
msgstr "Alchemist: The Tower Lord made me promise not to tell you — she was the one who had me sell you potions, even the Perpetual Potion. But it's too late now."

msgid "一位银白色长发、血色双瞳的魔塔之主，皮肤如寒冰般苍白，头顶生长着漆黑的螺旋形尖角。她身披暗纹流动的血色长袍，斜倚在由白骨雕成的王座上。左手轻搭扶手，指尖缠绕着幽蓝魔焰"
msgstr "A Tower Lord with silver-white hair and blood-red eyes. Her skin is pale as frost; spiraling black horns crown her head. She wears a crimson robe woven with shifting dark patterns, lounging on a throne carved from bone. Her left hand rests on the armrest, sapphire flames dancing at her fingertips."

msgid "看到来者，冰晶风暴在魔塔之主银发间盘旋凝结，猩红色瞳孔骤然收缩"
msgstr "As she sees you enter, an icy storm swirls in her silver hair. Her scarlet pupils contract sharply."

msgid "魔塔之主: 你终于来了，勇者，我等待着这一刻很久了。"
msgstr "Tower Lord: You've finally come, hero. I've been waiting for this moment."

msgid "魔塔之主: 那是你曾经送给我的戒指"
msgstr "Tower Lord: That ring — you gave it to me once."

msgid "魔塔之主: 不死不灭并不是祝福，于是我将我的心脏剖出赠予了巫师"
msgstr "Tower Lord: Immortality is no blessing. So I cut out my heart and gave it to the wizard."

msgid "魔塔之主: 我们之间只能有一个人能够离开。这是宿命。"
msgstr "Tower Lord: Only one of us can leave. That is fate."

msgid "魔塔之主: 你已经全部都想起来了，既然这样，你依然愿意放弃这场战斗吗？"
msgstr "Tower Lord: You remember everything now. Even so — would you still give up this fight?"

msgid "魔塔之主: 我愿意与你一同赴死"
msgstr "Tower Lord: I am willing to die with you."

msgid "魔塔之主: 一切终于可以结束了"
msgstr "Tower Lord: It can finally end."

msgid "徘徊的幽灵: 我好像……忘了很多东西，你能帮助我找回我的记忆吗？"
msgstr "Wandering Ghost: I seem to have... forgotten many things. Can you help me recover my memories?"

msgid "徘徊的幽灵: 我终于想起来了，谢谢你，帮我把我的孩子带回来，这是给你的报酬。"
msgstr "Wandering Ghost: I remember now. Thank you for bringing my child back. This is my reward."

msgid "徘徊的幽灵: 也许你可以听一听我的故事。"
msgstr "Wandering Ghost: Perhaps you'd like to hear my story."

msgid "他的一生穷困潦倒，年轻时被人以诬陷的罪名关入监狱，一生都为了赎罪券还债。还没有等到债务偿还，就被领主抓走赶到了前线"
msgstr "His was a life of poverty. Falsely accused, he was thrown in prison and spent his youth paying off indulgences. Before the debt was cleared, the lord seized him and sent him to the front lines."

msgid "十年之后，他带着一身的伤回到故乡，故乡已经尸横遍野，满是断垣残壁，他已经无处可去，一身都要与疾病和痛苦为伴"
msgstr "Ten years later, scarred and broken, he returned home — only to find a wasteland of corpses and rubble. He had nowhere to go, doomed to a life of sickness and suffering."

msgid "突然，他在路上听到了一声啼哭，他拨开石头，在废墟下发现了一个孩子"
msgstr "Then, on the road, he heard a cry. He pushed aside rubble and found a child beneath the ruins."

msgid "徘徊的幽灵: 我就是在那个时候捡到了费伦，我的孩子，他是我人生中的救赎，因为遇到了他，我才有勇气继续走下去"
msgstr "Wandering Ghost: That's when I found Ferren — my child. He was my salvation. Because of him, I found the courage to keep going."

msgid "徘徊的幽灵: 从此以后，我将费伦作为自己的孩子抚养长大，可惜好景不长，我居住的村子又遭受到了瘟疫，费伦离开了，我到处都找不到他"
msgstr "Wandering Ghost: I raised Ferren as my own. But it didn't last — plague struck our village. Ferren left, and I searched everywhere but couldn't find him."

msgid "他说到这里脸色一变，仿佛是回忆起来了什么恐怖的事情，很难想象一个身经百战的老兵会露出这样的神色"
msgstr "His face darkens, as if recalling something horrifying — a look that would shake even a battle-hardened veteran."

msgid "徘徊的幽灵: 于是我离开了村子到处寻找，不断地徘徊，不肯放弃。然而也正是我的坚持，我发现了可怕的事情"
msgstr "Wandering Ghost: So I left the village and wandered, searching, refusing to give up. And my persistence led me to a terrible truth."

msgid "当他回到故乡希望能够找到孩子的踪影，却发现在不远的地方又有了新的村落。他走进村子讨口水喝，却在村子里看到了熟悉的面孔"
msgstr "When he returned to his hometown hoping to find traces of his child, he discovered a new village nearby. He went in for a drink of water — and saw familiar faces."

msgid "徘徊的幽灵: 他们全部都复活了！但是他们都没有了之前的记忆。只有我，只有我还记得一切！"
msgstr "Wandering Ghost: They were all resurrected! But none of them remembered their past. Only I — only I remember everything!"

msgid "徘徊的幽灵: 我不敢想象这一切的发生就像做梦一般。难道我经受的苦难都是一场梦吗?那我身上的疤痕又是怎么解释？"
msgstr "Wandering Ghost: I can't believe this is real — it's like a dream. Was all my suffering just a dream? Then how do you explain my scars?"

msgid "意识到这一切的变故，他又回到瘟疫的村子，所有人都已经死了，神殿接管了那片土地，他们把瘟疫归于魔塔之主"
msgstr "Realizing what was happening, he went back to the plague village. Everyone was dead. The Temple had taken over the land, blaming the Tower Lord for the plague."

msgid "徘徊的幽灵: 我做了一个大胆的决定，我去墓地检查那些尸体，我要找到费伦"
msgstr "Wandering Ghost: I made a bold decision. I went to the graveyard to examine the bodies — I had to find Ferren."

msgid "但是那些尸体不翼而飞，那些病死的人，又出现在了另一个地方，失去了记忆"
msgstr "But the bodies had vanished. Those who died of disease had appeared somewhere else — memoryless."

msgid "徘徊的幽灵: 我真的疯了吗？最后我选择进入魔塔，在这里我知道了更多……但是我不能说，我没有疯……我真的没有疯"
msgstr "Wandering Ghost: Am I really insane? In the end, I entered the Magic Tower. Here, I learned more... but I can't tell you. I'm not crazy... I'm really not."

msgid "幽灵不再和你多说一句话"
msgstr "The ghost falls silent and will say no more."

msgid "徘徊的幽灵: 费伦，我的孩子，我带你回家吧。"
msgstr "Wandering Ghost: Ferren, my child. Let me take you home."

msgid "徘徊的幽灵: 谢谢。我很快就能想起来了。"
msgstr "Wandering Ghost: Thank you. I'll remember soon."

msgid "徘徊的幽灵: 我全部都想起来了！是那个可恶的巫师带走了我的孩子！不不是的，不是这样的，我全部都想起来了！"
msgstr "Wandering Ghost: I remember everything! That wretched wizard took my child! No — that's not right — I remember everything!"

msgid "徘徊的幽灵: 所有人都被骗了！这里是个巨大的谎言！你要快点逃出去！我也要，我也要……不不！！！我已经走不了了……"
msgstr "Wandering Ghost: Everyone's been deceived! This whole place is a lie! You have to escape! I'll escape too, I — NO!!! I can't leave anymore..."

msgid "徘徊的幽灵: 原来我已经死了，可是我的孩子……我的孩子啊，你在哪里？"
msgstr "Wandering Ghost: So I'm already dead... But my child... my child, where are you?"

msgid "勇士: 他已经陷入了疯狂"
msgstr "Brave: He's lost his mind."

msgid "徘徊的幽灵: 就连死亡也不是归宿，我们永远无法逃离"
msgstr "Wandering Ghost: Even death is no escape. We can never leave."
